</P>
<P>
   A9338 BC-NJ-PRIMARY-NYT 465 21:37 U A
</P>
<P>
   SHARP CONTRASTS EMERGE IN TWO NEW JERSEY RACES &QL;
</P>
<P>
   A9318 BC-MONTINI-COLUMN-AZR 671 21:28 R A
</P>
<P>
