 &HT;    Take ``The Route of Jean Lafitte,'' which goes between New
Orleans and Port Isabel, Texas, along the Gulf Coast. This
eight-day cruise, which starts in New Orleans and ends in
Galveston, Texas, starts at $1,730.
 &HT;    Other trips include ``Delta South,'' a four- or five-day trip
that goes round-trip from New Orleans.
 &HT;    The eight-day trip ends in Memphis, with stops at Natchez and
Vicksburg, Mississippi as well as Baton Rouge, Louisiana.
 &HT;    Prices range from $740 for the four-day trip to $1,730 for the
eight-day voyage.
 &HT;    Shore excursions, as well as tips, taxes and port charges are
included with the price.
