   NATIONAL
</P>
<P>
   BOMB _ DAYTON _ A 16-year-old male Little Miami High student is
in Warren County Juvenile Detention Center after allegedly bringing
a bomb to school. He's undergoing psychological testing and the
crime lab is testing the material. (Smith, Dayton Daily News).
</P>
