   &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; Contest time:  &LR; A lot of funny photographs are snapped on family
vacations. And that's why Hampton Inn, the chain of mid-priced
hotels, has launched its second annual Funniest Family Vacation
Photo Contest. For an entry form, go to the Web sites
www.hampton-inn.com or www.hampton-suites.com, fax a request to
214-953-3050 or send a self-addressed, stamped envelope to Hampton
Inn's Second Annual ``Funniest Family Vacation Photo Contest,''
2828 Routh St., Suite 680, Dallas, TX 75201. The grand prize winner
will receive an all-expenses-paid vacation, including air fare for
four, to Orlando, Washington, or Los Angeles; a nine-day stay in a
Hampton Inn; a rental car and the gasoline for it; $1,000 to spend;
and a year's supply of hotel-size soap and shampoo. Deadline for
entries is June 12, so snap to it.
