SEX-TV (Los Angeles) _ What do you get when you take Darren Star,
the creator of ``Melrose Place,'' and give him the content freedom
of HBO? Think of an R-rated ``Seinfeld'' from Elaine's perspective
and you'll have an idea of what's ahead. The result is ``Sex and
the City.'' By Keith Marder. 
. 
