the ``l'' lifestyle news file. For questions, contact Jimmy Johnson
at the Daily News, (818) 713-3695. 
. 
BOUTIQUE-CROSSDRESS (Los Angeles) _ Larry Schulz is more in touch
with his feminine side than the average guy. He's named it Gina,
and a couple of times a week he becomes her _ on the outside, not
only on the inside. The makeup artist whose sleight of hand
transforms Shultz into his towering alter-ego is Jim Bridges, owner
of a Studio City boutique that caters to a cross-dressing
clientele. By Jenifer Hanrahan. 
. 

