<HEADER>
A0793 &Cx1f; tad-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-BOTOX-COX-LIFE     06-02 1189
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-BOTOX-COX-LIFE </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    A shot at beauty: Toxin used to remove wrinkles
 &HT;    By Diane Lore
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
