<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-06-02 19:44 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0957 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RESCUE-AWARD-HNS &LR;      06-02 0895
