the Queen's estate in Norfolk, says W, which was a first for
 &UR; Prince Charles &LR; ' longtime pal. Parker Bowles often spends the night
at the Prince's London digs, but an overnight at the Queen's place
is ``a step forward toward bringing the British people around'' to
accept her special friendship with the Prince, says W.
</P>
