<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-INDONESIA-HABIBIE-NYT, which
moved in ``i'' news file.) 
c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``You know, I was always sitting on that side. The president was
always here. Now I am here!''
</P>
<P>
   _PRESIDENT B.J. HABIBIE of Indonesia.
</P>
</TEXT>
