textile and apparel business and operate as two separate public
companies. Daniel K. Frierson, the current chairman, president and
chief executive, will be chairman of both companies. William N. Fry
IV will become president and chief executive of the floor-covering
company, and George B. Smith will be president and chief executive
of the textile and apparel company.
</P>
