   (NYT1) SALT LAKE CITY -- June 2, 1998 -- BKN-JAZZ-SLOAN, 6-2 --
Bobbye and Jerry Sloan walking by their home in Wasatch Mountains.
Bobbye was diagnosed with breast cancer shortly after Jerry, the
coach of the Utah Jazz, faced his biggest challenge, the Chicago
Bulls. ``The situation she's gone through had made us more aware of
each other, a lot more,'' Jerry says. (George Frey/New York Times
Photo)
</P>
