<HEADLINE>
CITY COUNCILMAN WANTS PART OF BOULEVARD NAMED FOR RFK
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
(Will also move in the ``n'' California news file.) 
BY PETER HARTLAUB  
 c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
